41c514e3-c880-4f8b-9f0c-b51cfcd10de8.title: Bert
41c514e3-c880-4f8b-9f0c-b51cfcd10de8.text: Eeee, wha' shall I do! I'll mos' certainly lose tha job...

c8a01038-9527-462b-a17a-d8d6d9c46bff.title: <player>
c8a01038-9527-462b-a17a-d8d6d9c46bff.text: Lose your job? What's wrong, why?

d0e7c00b-e2fe-4176-9685-37055ae2b34a.title: Bert
d0e7c00b-e2fe-4176-9685-37055ae2b34a.text:
I w-w-work... over yon sand pit... and weeell... I
found... this... hand! T'were buried in't Sand!

options.text: Oh, you found a hand in the sand - that's nice for you.
Eww a hand, in the sand! Why haven't you told the authorities?

22ffca4a-692b-4845-aecb-e4eca33e3b6f.title: <player>
22ffca4a-692b-4845-aecb-e4eca33e3b6f.text: Oh, you found a hand in the sand - that's nice for you.

e73e5779-8c19-4d9f-b577-f1a30c501ce3.title: <player>
e73e5779-8c19-4d9f-b577-f1a30c501ce3.text:
Eww a hand, in the sand! Why haven't you told the
authorities?

fc032b26-2fd6-4d8d-9693-6743f0cb99c4.title: Bert
fc032b26-2fd6-4d8d-9693-6743f0cb99c4.text:
They's no' wha' they once was. Tha cap'ain o'the Guard
spends near all o'the time drunk in yon pub.

6ab90765-68c2-4758-9c8c-e4838b65c30a.title: <player>
6ab90765-68c2-4758-9c8c-e4838b65c30a.text:
Oh? The Guard Captain is drunk in the pub you say?
That's not good, what will you do?

7966fdc8-ca9d-4f16-92ee-38cb1949d632.text:
You do not meet all of the requirements to start
The Hand in the Sand quest.

ab98d146-24d6-4523-9aa8-b2e09d8700fa.title: Bert
ab98d146-24d6-4523-9aa8-b2e09d8700fa.text: Weeellll... do yer think yer could 'elp me?

6c967df9-ce56-4c4b-9381-95a02cbdf1db.title: <player>
6c967df9-ce56-4c4b-9381-95a02cbdf1db.text: I want no part in this!

38ccb9d7-0496-44b7-96a0-272e4a6c450d.title: <player>
38ccb9d7-0496-44b7-96a0-272e4a6c450d.text: Sure, I'll give you a hand.

9544ee88-0841-46b0-b152-8751c60a362d.title: Bert
9544ee88-0841-46b0-b152-8751c60a362d.text: ..... Nae, ye can 'ave the 'and as h'evidence.

b346b67f-e7ce-4345-83f1-b003afcf376d.text: Bert gives you a rather smelly, sand covered hand.

342e776d-2efa-4402-8fb6-192c4efe621f.title: Bert
342e776d-2efa-4402-8fb6-192c4efe621f.text:
P'raps tha smell will get t'Guard Cap'ain's nose out o'his
beer fer 2 seconds!

859d7b6d-4556-4257-a534-fe9bbe686514.title: Bert
859d7b6d-4556-4257-a534-fe9bbe686514.text: Did ye see yon Guard Capt'n 'bout hand?

503cc64a-9a40-4a60-9d43-132289af91cb.title: <player>
503cc64a-9a40-4a60-9d43-132289af91cb.text: Not at the moment, but I will be seeing him soon.

037a2aee-6a24-42b7-b1c2-3a88cc9c6a9d.title: <player>
037a2aee-6a24-42b7-b1c2-3a88cc9c6a9d.text: Err, I kind of... lost my grip on it...

4b9189ba-23dc-4bec-89cf-33076328355c.title: Bert
4b9189ba-23dc-4bec-89cf-33076328355c.text:
Thank t'gods! I tho' I searched up another when I been
pickin' this'un up outside... Take tha' blasted thing to
yon Guard Captain quick sharp.

4fc7221c-ef96-4a40-95be-1cec47b1ccc0.title: <player>
4fc7221c-ef96-4a40-95be-1cec47b1ccc0.text: Thanks Bert, I'll go see the Guard Captain right now.

109cdd27-decf-4ed4-a278-5868d259d7e2.title: Bert
109cdd27-decf-4ed4-a278-5868d259d7e2.text: Did ye see yon Guard Capt'n 'bout hand?

b9086c58-3c0f-4192-81a1-3f279c8678ff.title: <player>
b9086c58-3c0f-4192-81a1-3f279c8678ff.text:
Yes, the Guard Captain said to see the wizards in the
guild.

3eb7fd66-9863-46d3-8cd0-c4c84db8a321.title: Bert
3eb7fd66-9863-46d3-8cd0-c4c84db8a321.text:
So why you hangin' abou' 'ere then? Go ring t'bell at
t'mage guild just over yonder!

995180c0-e848-461c-aa8b-84238765b5a8.title: <player>
995180c0-e848-461c-aa8b-84238765b5a8.text: It seems to have slipped through my fingers!

c9adb3be-8a9b-497b-95b6-d734082aecab.title: Bert
c9adb3be-8a9b-497b-95b6-d734082aecab.text:
Thank t'gods! I tho' I was bein invaded by undead
'ands from t'sand when I found this'un! Take i' to tha
mage guild and ring tha' bell to talk ta someone.

8256f01d-b704-485f-845e-c840420c2f7a.title: <player>
8256f01d-b704-485f-845e-c840420c2f7a.text:
Thanks Bert, I'm off to see the wizards, the wonderful
wizards of Yanille!

e1c44e8b-2c9c-49b2-b44b-307d4edf432e.title: <player>
e1c44e8b-2c9c-49b2-b44b-307d4edf432e.text:
I dug up quite a lot about the hand. Can you tell me
about your job?

10fbec37-4830-4269-a39b-8190e25b8123.title: Bert
10fbec37-4830-4269-a39b-8190e25b8123.text:
Sand! Lots o' sand! Me boss be Sandy o' Sandy's Sand
Corp based in Brimhaven on tha isle of Karamja an' I
hauls sand fr' there to yon sand pit.

9a3e0875-f5cf-4a15-b8c3-842080c34dde.title: Bert
9a3e0875-f5cf-4a15-b8c3-842080c34dde.text:
I's looong harrrrd hours, bu' keeps me busy, y'know
what tha say! 'Idle hands'r Zamorak's tools.'

ae6e4d6f-70a8-49f5-843b-dcf2cd031724.title: <player>
ae6e4d6f-70a8-49f5-843b-dcf2cd031724.text:
So you're employed by Sandy's Sand Corp in
Brimhaven. Have you changed your hours recently?

50c4f135-7fd7-49ef-a82b-e94f5820357d.title: Bert
50c4f135-7fd7-49ef-a82b-e94f5820357d.text:
Nae! See fer yersel', here's a copy o' me rota tha' be
held a' head office - yer can looksee iffin ye talk t'
Sandy, me boss.

4622a14f-ecf8-42d9-80ac-fc8bd654cf4e.title: <player>
4622a14f-ecf8-42d9-80ac-fc8bd654cf4e.text:
Thanks for the Rota Bert. I'll go check for the original
with Sandy in Brimhaven.

9b0d97ab-27ad-4c9a-b2c7-1b30860c4910.title: Bert
9b0d97ab-27ad-4c9a-b2c7-1b30860c4910.text:
Ey'up <player>. Did yer see Sandy in Brimhaven
'bout me rota?

639b08e0-49a5-41eb-b5bf-3a2591714d0a.title: <player>
639b08e0-49a5-41eb-b5bf-3a2591714d0a.text: No, I'll fit it in my schedule somewhere soon.

b0e2bc76-5676-4015-b2f0-3002bf397bf3.title: <player>
b0e2bc76-5676-4015-b2f0-3002bf397bf3.text: Err, no, I kind of... lost it...

352a5661-2200-4033-af3d-b8f2acfb6066.title: Bert
352a5661-2200-4033-af3d-b8f2acfb6066.text:
Lucky fer yorn tha' I's made a copy then ain't it, 'ere
'ave another.

77561de6-46b3-4f09-837f-128ff0380da6.text:
Maybe you should have the rota from Sandy's desk with you before
confronting Bert.

2097c99a-0add-4acc-b15f-54840f8e328c.title: <player>
2097c99a-0add-4acc-b15f-54840f8e328c.text:
I managed to get a copy of the original rota. Your
hours changed a week ago!

c3037198-3de6-4be2-a61a-df56a28cf304.title: Bert
c3037198-3de6-4be2-a61a-df56a28cf304.text:
Nae! Nae! I din't remember tha', bu'... hmmm, aye...
tha' migh' be it...

28a8d411-4160-4a21-8ab0-8c611407f57b.title: <player>
28a8d411-4160-4a21-8ab0-8c611407f57b.text:
What? Give me a hand here, I'm having a hard time
understanding how you don't remember changing
hours!

903e31d3-4dcf-4926-bba4-f0af79054019.title: Bert
903e31d3-4dcf-4926-bba4-f0af79054019.text:
I's all be tha wizard's fault! Tha magic leaks fr'm yon
magic guild I tells yer! Tha's why this weirrrrd scroll
appeareded a week ago!

198ec88c-3500-48e3-a35f-627592930d0b.title: <player>
198ec88c-3500-48e3-a35f-627592930d0b.text:
A scroll appeared? Can I take a look at it while you look
at the rotas?

30d5b2a4-f813-4440-a78b-cf78bba08903.title: Bert
30d5b2a4-f813-4440-a78b-cf78bba08903.text:
O'course <player>, le's be 'avin'yon rota and 'ere be
tha scroll, yer be takin' it back ta those inferrrnal
wizards quick sharp!

0249d8fa-59ea-4fb6-9b2c-b1d9a522a34e.title: Bert
0249d8fa-59ea-4fb6-9b2c-b1d9a522a34e.text:
I be hopin' tha search is goin' well... are tha wizard's
owning up ta anythin' yet?

5c831781-a04c-4eb2-b118-21a4c2695b99.title: <player>
5c831781-a04c-4eb2-b118-21a4c2695b99.text:
I've found out a lot and will let you know when it's all
over.

aa401e20-e7ba-477f-b95a-2d02bb2fc476.title: <player>
aa401e20-e7ba-477f-b95a-2d02bb2fc476.text: Err, no, I kind of... lost the scroll...

48957213-969c-4f7c-94a8-fd33cee787b0.title: Bert
48957213-969c-4f7c-94a8-fd33cee787b0.text: I's be seein' ya drop it on tha' way out, 'ere 'tis.

c793c00f-5ae3-4ec0-9baf-365ab47bbc49.title: Bert
c793c00f-5ae3-4ec0-9baf-365ab47bbc49.text:
I be hopin' tha search is goin' well... are tha wizard's
owning up ta anythin' yet?

fd475d7c-a98d-47b2-89d0-b9cfad47d490.title: <player>
fd475d7c-a98d-47b2-89d0-b9cfad47d490.text:
I've found out a lot and will let you know when it's all
over.
